                                                <label style="margin-left:5px;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-9-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mn>1</mn></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-236" style="width: 0.64em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.503em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.414em, 1000.41em, 2.37em, -999.998em); top: -2.229em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-237"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-238" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">1</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.234em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.053em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 0.947em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mn>1</mn></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-9">1</script></span></p>
</label>

                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="col-sm-12 row questionOption">
                                        <div class="input-group" style="align-items: center;">
                                            <div class="input-group-prepend">
                                                <span class="input-group-text">C</span>

                                    <div class="row solveText" style="display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4;">
                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-11-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>&amp;#x2264;</mo><mi>cos</mi><mo>&amp;#x2061;</mo><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mrow><mo>(</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>x</mi></mfrac><mo>)</mo></mrow></mrow><mo>&amp;#x2264;</mo><mn>1</mn></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-243" style="width: 7.666em; top: -2.047em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-244"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-245" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">−</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-246" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">1</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-247" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">≤</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-248" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">cos</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-249"></span><span class="texatom" id="MathJax-Span-250" style="padding-left: 0.166em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-251"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-252"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-253" style="vertical-align: 0em;"><span style="font-family: MathJax_Size1;">(</span></span><span class="mfrac" id="MathJax-Span-254"><span style="display: inline-block; margin-left: -0.162em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-255" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">1</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.904em, 1000.49em, 1.191em, -999.998em); top: -1.268em; left: 0em;"><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; <p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-12-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi>x</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-260" style="width: 0.576em; width: 0px; height: 1.969em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.048em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 0.653em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mi>x</mi></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-12">x</script></span> এর মান যত 0 এর কাছাকাছি যাবে, <span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-13-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mi>x</mi></mfrac></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-263" style="width: 0.822em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.658em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.986em, 1000.66em, 2.461em, -999.998em); top: -1.965em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-264"><span class="mfrac" id="MathJax-Span-265"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.535em; height: 0px; margin-right: 0.125em; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.904em, 1000.53em, 1.191em, -999.998em); top: -1.268em; left: 0em;"><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: 0em; border-top: 1.5px solid; width: 0.535em; height: 0px;"></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.068em;"></span></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.969em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.497em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.602em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mi>x</mi></mfrac></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-13">\frac{1}{x}</script></span> এর মান তত দ্রুত পরিবর্তিত হবে। তখন সুনির্দিষ্ট কোনো মান না এনে&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-14-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>1</mn></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-268" style="width: 1.314em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.068em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.191em, 1000.99em, 2.174em, -999.998em); top: -1.965em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-269"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-270" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">−</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-271" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">1</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; </span>

                                        <div class="serial"><span>Question 3</span></div>

font-family: MathJax_Main;">′</span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 3.988em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-302" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">(</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-303" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">x</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-304" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">)</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-19-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>f</mi><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>(</mo><mn>15</mn><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>)</mo></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-305" style="width: 2.647em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 2.163em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.38em, 1002.05em, 2.61em, -999.998em);                                         </div>

                                    <div class="row solveText" style="display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4;">
                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p>Lagrange’s mean value theorem&nbsp;অনুসারে, এমন একটি বিন্দু&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; padding-left: 0.207em;">+</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-393" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">f<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.084em;"></span></span><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-394" style="padding-left: 0.166em;"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-395" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">(</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-396" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">6</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-397" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">)</span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-398" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-399" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">9</span><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-400"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.699em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.199em, 1000.37em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-401" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">f<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.084em;"></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -4.383em; left: 0.453em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-402" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">′</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-403" style="padding-left: 0.166em;"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-404" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">(</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-405" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">c</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-406" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">)</span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-407" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">−</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-408" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">2</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.969em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.547em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.952em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><msup><mi mathvariant="normal">f</mi><mi class="MJX-variant" mathvariant="normal">′</mi></msup><mrow><mo>(</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">c</mi><mo>)</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">f</mi><mrow><mo>(</mo><mn>15</mn><mo>)</mo></mrow><mo>−</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">f</mi><mrow><mo>(</mo><mn>6</mn><mo>)</mo></mrow></mrow><mrow><mn>15</mn><mo>−</mo><mn>6</mn></mrow></mfrac><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><mn>9</mn><msup><mi mathvariant="normal">f</mi><mi class="MJX-variant" mathvariant="normal">′</mi></msup><mrow><mo>(</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">c</mi><mo>)</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">f</mi><mrow><mo>(</mo><mn>15</mn><mo>)</mo></mrow><mo>−</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">f</mi><mrow><mo>(</mo><mn>6</mn><mo>)</mo></mrow><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">f</mi><mrow><mo>(</mo><mn>15</mn><mo>)</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><mn>9</mn><msup><mi mathvariant="normal">f</mi><mi class="MJX-variant" mathvariant="normal">′</mi></msup><mrow><mo>(</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">c</mi><mo>)</mo></mrow><mo>+</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">f</mi><mrow><mo>(</mo><mn>6</mn><mo>)</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><mn>9</mn><msup><mi mathvariant="normal">f</mi><mi class="MJX-variant" mathvariant="normal">′</mi></msup><mrow><mo>(</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">c</mi><mo>)</mo></mrow><mo>−</mo><mn>2</mn></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-25">\rm f^\prime\left(c\right)=\frac{f\left(15\right)-f\left(6\right)}{15-6}\Rightarrow9f^\prime\left(c\right)=f\left(15\right)-f\left(6\right)\Rightarrow f\left(15\right)=9f^\prime\left(c\right)+f\left(6\right)=9f^\prime\left(c\right)-2</script></span>&nbsp;</p>

<p>এখন,&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-26-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><msup><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>f</mi><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mi class=&quot;MJX-variant&quot; mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>&amp;#x2032;</mi></mrow></msup><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>(</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>x</mi><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>)</mo></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-409" style="width: 2.01em; font-family: MathJax_Main;">x</span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.904em, 1001.6em, 1.191em, -999.998em); top: -1.268em; left: 0em;"><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: 0em; border-top: 1.5px solid; width: 1.6em; height: 0px;"></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.068em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-560" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-561" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">−</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-562" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">1</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.051em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.948em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 2.103em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mfrac><mi mathvariant="normal">d</mi><mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">d</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">x</mi></mrow></mfrac><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><msup><mi>cos</mi><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msup><mo>⁡</mo><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mi>sin</mi><mo>⁡</mo><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mi mathvariant="normal">x</mi></mrow></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow></mrow></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><mo>−</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><msqrt><mn>1</mn><mo>−</mo><msup><mi>sin</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>⁡</mo><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mi mathvariant="normal">x</mi></mrow></msqrt></mfrac><mo>⋅</mo><mi>cos</mi><mo>⁡</mo><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mi mathvariant="normal">x</mi></mrow><mo>=</mo><mo>−</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi>cos</mi><mo>⁡</mo><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mi mathvariant="normal">x</mi></mrow></mrow><mrow><mi>cos</mi><mo>⁡</mo><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mi mathvariant="normal">x</mi></mrow></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-35">\rm \frac{d}{dx}\left(\cos^{-1}{\left(\sin{x}\right)}\right)=-\frac{1}{\sqrt{1-\sin^2{x}}}\cdot\cos{x}=-\frac{\cos{x}}{\cos{x}}=-1</script></span></p>
</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="row questionBlock">

                            <div class="row question">
                                <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial"><span>Question 5</span></div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">

<p>ধরি,&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-49-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi>&amp;#x03B8;</mi><mo>+</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>h</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mi>&amp;#x03C0;</mi><mn>2</mn></mfrac></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-883" style="width: 4.346em; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(2.953em, 1002.3em, 4.592em, -999.998em); top: -3.195em; left: 50%; margin-left: -1.145em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-950"><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-951"><span style="display: inline-block; font-family: MathJax_Main;">4</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.904em, 1002.62em, 1.191em, -999.998em); width: 0px; height: 1.068em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-961" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mfrac" id="MathJax-Span-962" style="padding-left: 0.289em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.494em; height: 0px; margin-right: 0.125em; margin-left: 0.125em;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1000.29em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.424em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.162em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-963" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">1</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1000.33em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -3.645em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.162em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-964" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">2</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.904em, 1000.49em, 1.191em, -999.998em); top: -1.268em; left: 0em;"><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: 0em; border-top: 1.5px solid; width: 0.494em; height: 0px;"></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.068em;"></span></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.174em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -1.648em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 3.302em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mo>∴</mo><munder><mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">l</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">i</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">m</mi></mrow><mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">h</mi><mo stretchy="false">→</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow></munder><mfrac><mrow><mn>1</mn><mo>−</mo><mi>cos</mi><mo>⁡</mo><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mi mathvariant="normal">h</mi></mrow></mrow><msup><mi mathvariant="normal">h</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>2</mn><msup><mi>sin</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>⁡</mo><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mfrac><mi mathvariant="normal">h</mi><mn>2</mn></mfrac></mrow></mrow><mrow><msup><mrow><mo>(</mo><mfrac><mi mathvariant="normal">h</mi><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mo>)</mo></mrow><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>⋅</mo><mn>4</mn></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-53">\rm \therefore \underset{h\rightarrow0}{lim}\frac{1-\cos{h}}{h^2}=\frac{2\sin^2{\frac{h}{2}}}{\left(\frac{h}{2}\right)^2\cdot4}=\frac{1}{2}</script></span>&nbsp;</p>
</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                            <div class="row question">
                                <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial"><span>Question 8</span></div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-60-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><munder><mrow><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>l</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>i</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>m</mi></mrow><mrow><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>x</mi><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>&amp;#x2192;</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow></munder><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mfrac><mrow><mn>1</mn><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mi>cos</mi><mo>&amp;#x2061;</mo><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mn>7</mn><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>x</mi></mrow></mrow><mrow><mn>3</mn><msup><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mo>?</mo></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1083" style="width: 7.64em; <p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-66-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>&amp;#x21D2;</mo><munder><mrow><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>l</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>i</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>m</mi></mrow><mrow><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>x</mi><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>&amp;#x2192;</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow></munder><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mfrac><mrow><mn>7</mn><mi>sin</mi><mo>&amp;#x2061;</mo><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mn>7</mn><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>x</mi></mrow></mrow><mrow><mn>6</mn><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>x</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>&amp;#x21D2;</mo><munder><mrow><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>l</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>i</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>m</mi></mrow><mrow><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>x</mi><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>&amp;#x2192;</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow></munder><mfrac><mrow><mn>49</mn><mi>cos</mi><mo>&amp;#x2061;</mo><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mn>7</mn><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>x</mi></mrow></mrow><mn>6</mn></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>49</mn><mn>6</mn></mfrac></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1159" style="width: 14.182em;                                     <div class="row solveText" style="display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4;">
                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-73-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><msup><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>x</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>y</mi></msup><mo>=</mo><msup><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>y</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>x</mi></msup><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>&amp;#x21D2;</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>y</mi><mi>ln</mi><mo>&amp;#x2061;</mo><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>x</mi></mrow><mo>=</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>x</mi><mi>ln</mi><mo>&amp;#x2061;</mo><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>y</mi></mrow><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>&amp;#x21D2;</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi>ln</mi><mo>&amp;#x2061;</mo><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>x</mi></mrow></mrow><mrow><mi>ln</mi><mo>&amp;#x2061;</mo><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>y</mi></mrow></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>x</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>y</mi></mfrac></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1257" style="width: 15.863em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 12.994em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.945em, 1012.99em, 2.625em, -999.998em); top: -1.965em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1258"><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-1259"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.986em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1000.53em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1260" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">x</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -4.383em; left: 0.535em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1261" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">y</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1262" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-1263" style="padding-left: 0.289em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.986em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1000.49em, 4.346em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1264" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">y</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -4.383em; left: 0.535em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1265" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">x</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1266" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">⇒</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1267" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">y</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1268" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.166em;">ln</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1269"></span><span class="texatom" id="MathJax-Span-1270" style="padding-left: 0.166em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1271"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1272" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">x</span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1273" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1274" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">x</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1275" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.166em;">ln</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1276"></span><span class="texatom" id="MathJax-Span-1277" style="padding-left: 0.166em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1278"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1279" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">y</span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1280" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">⇒</span><span class="mfrac" id="MathJax-Span-1281" style="padding-left: 0.289em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.232em; height: 0px; margin-right: 0.125em; margin-left: 0.125em;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.404em, 1001.11em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.424em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.572em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1282"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1283" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">ln</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1284" style="font-size: 70.7%;"></span><span class="texatom" id="MathJax-Span-1285" style="padding-left: 0.166em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1286"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1287" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">x</span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.404em, 1001.11em, 4.305em, -999.998em); top: -3.645em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.572em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1288"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1289" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">ln</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1290" style="font-size: 70.7%;"></span><span class="texatom" id="MathJax-Span-1291" style="padding-left: 0.166em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1292"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1293" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">y</span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.904em, 1001.23em, 1.191em, -999.998em); top: -1.268em; left: 0em;"><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: 0em; border-top: 1.5px solid; width: 1.232em; height: 0px;"></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.068em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1294" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mfrac" id="MathJax-Span-1295" style="padding-left: 0.289em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.494em; height: 0px; margin-right: 0.125em; margin-left: 0.125em;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.609em, 1000.37em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.424em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.203em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1296" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">x</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.609em, 1000.37em, 4.305em, -999.998em); top: -3.686em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.203em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1297" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">y</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.904em, 1000.49em, 1.191em, -999.998em); top: -1.268em; left: 0em;"><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: 0em; border-top: 1.5px solid; width: 0.494em; height: 0px;"></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.068em;"></span></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.969em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.698em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.802em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><msup><mi mathvariant="normal">x</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">y</mi></msup><mo>=</mo><msup><mi mathvariant="normal">y</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">x</mi></msup><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">y</mi><mi>ln</mi><mo>⁡</mo><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mi mathvariant="normal">x</mi></mrow><mo>=</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">x</mi><mi>ln</mi><mo>⁡</mo><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mi mathvariant="normal">y</mi></mrow><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi>ln</mi><mo>⁡</mo><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mi mathvariant="normal">x</mi></mrow></mrow><mrow><mi>ln</mi><mo>⁡</mo><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mi mathvariant="normal">y</mi></mrow></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mi mathvariant="normal">x</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">y</mi></mfrac></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-73">\rm x^y=y^x\Rightarrow y\ln{x}=x\ln{y}\Rightarrow\frac{\ln{x}}{\ln{y}}=\frac{x}{y} </script></span></p>
</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="row questionBlock">

                            <div class="row question">
                                <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial"><span>Question 10</span></div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-74-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>y</mi><mo>=</mo><msup><mi>tan</mi><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msup><mo>&amp;#x2061;</mo><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><msqrt><mfrac><mrow><mn>1</mn><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>c</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>o</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>s</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>x</mi></mrow><mrow><mn>1</mn><mo>+</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>c</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>o</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>s</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>x</mi></mrow></mfrac></msqrt></mrow></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1298" style="width: 9.801em;                                         <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>

                                        <div class="serial"><span>Question 14</span></div>

                                    <div class="row solveText" style="display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4;">

vertical-align: -0.948em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 2.502em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mo>∴</mo><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">y</mi><mn>4</mn></msub><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>17</mn><msup><mi mathvariant="normal">a</mi><mn>4</mn></msup><mo>×</mo><mn>3</mn><mo>!</mo><msup><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow><mn>3</mn></msup></mrow><msup><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">a</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">x</mi><mo>+</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">b</mi></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow><mn>4</mn></msup></mfrac><mo>∴</mo><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">y</mi><mn>5</mn></msub><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>17</mn><msup><mi mathvariant="normal">a</mi><mn>5</mn></msup><mn>4</mn><mo>!</mo></mrow><msup><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">a</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">x</mi><mo>+</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">b</mi></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow><mn>5</mn></msup></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>408</mn><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><msup><mi mathvariant="normal">a</mi><mn>5</mn></msup></mrow><msup><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">a</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">x</mi><mo>+</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">b</mi></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow><mn>5</mn></msup></mfrac></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-108">\rm \therefore y_4=\frac{17a^4\times3!\left(-1\right)^3}{\left(ax+b\right)^4}\therefore y_5=\frac{17a^54!}{\left(ax+b\right)^5}=\frac{408\ a^5}{\left(ax+b\right)^5}</script></span></p>
</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                                    <div class="row solveText" style="display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4;">
                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p>স্পর্শক ও অভিলম্বের ছেদবিন্দু&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-118-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>(</mo><mn>3</mn><mo>,</mo><mn>12</mn><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>)</mo></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-2199" style="width: 2.707em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 2.215em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.109em, 1002.13em, 2.338em, -999.998em); top: -1.965em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-2200"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-2201" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">(</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-2202" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">3</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-2203" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">,</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-2204" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.166em;">12</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-2205" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">)</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.969em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.348em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.302em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mn>3</mn><mo>,</mo><mn>12</mn><mo stretchy="false">)</mo></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-118">\rm (3,12)</script></span>&nbsp;</p>

<p>ধরি,&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-119-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>f</mi><mrow><mo>(</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>x</mi><mo>)</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>a</mi><msup><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>b</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>c</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-2206" style="width: 8.609em;                                         <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>

class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-2476" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">−</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-2477" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-2483" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">0</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-2484" style="font-family: MathJax_AMS; padding-left: 0.289em;">∴</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-2485" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">x</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-2486" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-2487" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">e</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.174em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.647em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.952em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><mi>ln</mi><mo>⁡</mo><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mi mathvariant="normal">y</mi></mrow><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mi mathvariant="normal">x</mi></mfrac><mi>ln</mi><mo>⁡</mo><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mi mathvariant="normal">x</mi></mrow><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mi mathvariant="normal">y</mi></mfrac><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mfrac><mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">d</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">y</mi></mrow><mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">d</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">x</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><msup><mi mathvariant="normal">x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></mfrac><mo>−</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><msup><mi mathvariant="normal">x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></mfrac><mi>ln</mi><mo>⁡</mo><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mi mathvariant="normal">x</mi></mrow><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">d</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">y</mi></mrow><mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">d</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">x</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><msup><mi mathvariant="normal">x</mi><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mi mathvariant="normal">x</mi></mfrac></msup><mfrac><mn>1</mn><msup><mi mathvariant="normal">x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></mfrac><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mn>1</mn><mo>−</mo><mi>ln</mi><mo>⁡</mo><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mi mathvariant="normal">x</mi></mrow></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>−</mo><mi>ln</mi><mo>⁡</mo><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mi mathvariant="normal">x</mi></mrow><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn><mo>∴</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">x</mi><mo>=</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">e</mi></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-134">\rm \Rightarrow\ln{y}=\frac{1}{x}\ln{x}\Rightarrow\frac{1}{y}\ \frac{dy}{dx}=\frac{1}{x^2}-\frac{1}{x^2}\ln{x}\Rightarrow\frac{dy}{dx}=x^\frac{1}{x}\frac{1}{x^2}\left(1-\ln{x}\right)=0\Rightarrow1-\ln{x}=0\therefore x=e</script></span></p>
</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="row questionBlock">

                            <div class="row question">
                                <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial"><span>Question 17</span></div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p>সমকোণী ত্রিভুজের সমকোণ সংলগ্ন একটি বাহুর দৈর্ঘ্য 3 একক এবং a একক দৈর্ঘ্যের অপর বাহু সময়ের সাথে পরিবর্তিত হলে ত্রিভুজটির অতিভূজের দৈর্ঘ্য পরিবর্তনের হার a বাহুর দৈর্ঘ্য পরিবর্তনের কত গুণ?</p>

                                        </div>

</label>

                                        </div>

                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>

position: relative; width: 0.945em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.24em, 1000.45em, 4.182em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-2739" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">6</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -4.424em; left: 0.494em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-2740" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">2</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.609em, 1003.08em, 3.895em, -999.998em); top: -4.752em; left: 0.986em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 3.076em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; font-family: MathJax_Main; top: -4.014em; left: -0.08em;">−<span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; font-family: MathJax_Main; top: -4.014em; left: 2.379em;">−<span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="font-family: MathJax_Main; position: absolute; top: -4.014em; left: 0.371em;">−<span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="font-family: MathJax_Main; position: absolute; top: -4.014em; left: 0.904em;">−<span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="font-family: MathJax_Main; position: absolute; top: -4.014em; left: 1.395em;">−<span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="font-family: MathJax_Main; position: absolute; top: -4.014em; left: 1.887em;">−<span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.035em, 1001.03em, 4.51em, -999.998em); top: -4.178em; left: 0em;"><span style="font-family: MathJax_Size1;">√</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-2741" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-2742" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">2</span><span class="msqrt" id="MathJax-Span-2743"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.928em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.24em, 1000.95em, 4.182em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0.822em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-2744"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-2745" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">10</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.609em, 1001.11em, 3.895em, -999.998em); top: -4.588em; left: 0.822em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.109em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; font-family: MathJax_Main; top: -4.014em; left: -0.08em;">−<span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; font-family: MathJax_Main; top: -4.014em; left: 0.412em;">−<span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.076em, 1000.86em, 4.346em, -999.998em); top: -4.055em; left: 0em;"><span style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">√</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-2746" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">m</span><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-2747"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.355em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1000.37em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-2748" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">s</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -4.383em; left: 0.412em;"><span class="texatom" id="MathJax-Span-2749"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-2750"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-2751" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">−</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-2752" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">1</span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.174em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.497em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.952em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mfrac><mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">d</mi><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mover><mi mathvariant="normal">s</mi><mo stretchy="false">→</mo></mover></mrow><mrow><mo>(</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">t</mi><mo>)</mo></mrow></mrow><mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">d</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">t</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mover><mi mathvariant="normal">v</mi><mo stretchy="false">→</mo></mover></mrow><mo>=</mo><mn>2</mn><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mover><mi mathvariant="normal">i</mi><mo stretchy="false">^</mo></mover></mrow><mo>+</mo><mn>6</mn><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mover><mi mathvariant="normal">j</mi><mo stretchy="false">^</mo></mover></mrow><mo>∴</mo><mrow><mo>|</mo><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mover><mi mathvariant="normal">v</mi><mo stretchy="false">→</mo></mover></mrow><mo>|</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><msqrt><msup><mn>2</mn><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><msup><mn>6</mn><mn>2</mn></msup></msqrt><mo>=</mo><mn>2</mn><msqrt><mn>10</mn></msqrt><mi mathvariant="normal">m</mi><msup><mi mathvariant="normal">s</mi><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msup></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-148">\rm \frac{d\vec{s}\left(t\right)}{dt}=\vec{v}=2\hat{i}+6\hat{j}\therefore\left|\vec{v}\right|=\sqrt{2^2+6^2}=2\sqrt{10}ms^{-1}</script></span></p>
</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="row questionBlock">

                            <div class="row question">
                                <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial"><span>Question 19</span></div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p>একটি পুকুরের একটি বৃত্তাকার ঢেউ এর পরিধি বৃদ্ধির হার <span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-149-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>a</mi><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>m</mi><msup><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>s</mi><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msup></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-2753" style="width: 3.653em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 2.982em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.306em, 1002.98em, 2.349em, -999.998em);                                     <div class="row solveText" style="display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4;">
                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p>পরিধি s হলে,&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-154-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>s</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>2</mn><mi>&amp;#x03C0;</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>r</mi><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>&amp;#x21D2;</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>d</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>s</mi></mrow><mrow><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>d</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>t</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mn>2</mn><mi>&amp;#x03C0;</mi><mfrac><mrow><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>d</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>r</mi></mrow><mrow><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>d</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>t</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>&amp;#x21D2;</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>a</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>2</mn><mi>&amp;#x03C0;</mi><mfrac><mrow><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>d</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>r</mi></mrow><mrow><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>d</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>t</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo>&amp;#x2234;</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>d</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>r</mi></mrow><mrow><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>d</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>t</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>a</mi><mrow><mn>2</mn><mi>&amp;#x03C0;</mi></mrow></mfrac></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-2790" style="width: 19.551em; </span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                                    <div class="row solveText" style="display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4;">
                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p>একটি x ও অন্যটি&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-155-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>(</mo><mn>12</mn><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>x</mi><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>)</mo><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mo>&amp;#x2234;</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>y</mi><mo>=</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>x</mi><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mn>12</mn><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>x</mi></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-2841" style="width: 11.314em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 9.264em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.314em, 1009.18em, 2.543em, -999.998em); top: -2.17em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-2842"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-2843" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">(</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-2844" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">12</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-2845" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">−</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-2846" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">x</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-2847" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">)</span><span class="mtext" id="MathJax-Span-2848" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">&nbsp;</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-2849" style="font-family: MathJax_AMS; padding-left: 0.289em;">∴</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-2850" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">y</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-2851" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-2852" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">x</span><span class="mtext" id="MathJax-Span-2853" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">&nbsp;</span><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-2854" style="padding-left: 0.166em;"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-2855" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">(</span><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-2856"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-2857" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">12</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-2858" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">−</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-2859" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">x</span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-2860" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">)</span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.174em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.348em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.302em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mn>12</mn><mo>−</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">x</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mo>∴</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">y</mi><mo>=</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">x</mi><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mn>12</mn><mo>−</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">x</mi></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-155">\rm (12-x)\ \therefore y=x\ \left(12-x\right)</script></span>&nbsp;</p>

<p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-156-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>&amp;#x21D2;</mo><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>y</mi><mo>=</mo><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><msup><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mn>12</mn><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>x</mi><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>&amp;#x21D2;</mo><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><msup><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>y</mi><mi class=&quot;MJX-variant&quot; mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>&amp;#x2032;</mi></msup><mo>=</mo><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>2</mn><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>12</mn></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-2861" style="width: 16.109em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 13.199em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.027em, 1013.16em, 2.297em, -999.998em); top: -1.965em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-2862"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-2863" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">⇒</span><span class="mtext" id="MathJax-Span-2864" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">&nbsp;</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-2865" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">y</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-2866" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-2867" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">−</span><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-2868"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.945em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1000.53em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-2869" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">x</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -4.383em; left: 0.535em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-2870" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">2</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-2871" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">+</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-2872" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">12</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-2873" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">x</span><span class="mtext" id="MathJax-Span-2874" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">&nbsp;</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-2875" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">⇒</span><span class="mtext" id="MathJax-Span-2876" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">&nbsp;</span><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-2877"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.781em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1000.49em, 4.346em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-2878" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">y</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -4.383em; left: 0.535em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-2879" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">′</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-2880" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-2881" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">−</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-2882" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">2</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-2883" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">x</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-2884" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">+</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-2885" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">12</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.969em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.297em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.353em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mi mathvariant="normal">y</mi><mo>=</mo><mo>−</mo><msup><mi mathvariant="normal">x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mn>12</mn><mi mathvariant="normal">x</mi><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><msup><mi mathvariant="normal">y</mi><mi class="MJX-variant" mathvariant="normal">′</mi></msup><mo>=</mo><mo>−</mo><mn>2</mn><mi mathvariant="normal">x</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>12</mn></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-156">\rm \Rightarrow\ y=-x^2+12x\ \Rightarrow\ y^\prime=-2x+12</script></span></p>

<p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-157-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><msup><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>y</mi><mi class=&quot;MJX-variant&quot; mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>&amp;#x2032;</mi></msup><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>&amp;#x21D2;</mo><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>6</mn></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-2886" style="width: 7.379em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 6.027em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.068em, 1005.99em, 2.297em, -999.998em); top: -1.965em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-2887"><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-2888"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.781em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1000.49em, 4.346em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-2889" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">y</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -4.383em; left: 0.535em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-2890" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">′</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-2891" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-2892" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">0</span><span class="mtext" id="MathJax-Span-2893" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">&nbsp;</span><span class="mtext" id="MathJax-Span-2894" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">&nbsp;</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-2895" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.297em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.252em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><msup><mi mathvariant="normal">y</mi><mi class="MJX-variant" mathvariant="normal">′</mi></msup><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mi mathvariant="normal">x</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>6</mn></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-157">\rm y^\prime=0\ \ \Rightarrow\ x=6</script></span></p>

<p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-158-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2234;</mo></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-2900" style="width: 0.658em;                                         <br>

                            <div class="row question">
                                <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial"><span>Question 23</span></div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">

                                        <div class="serial"><span>Question 24</span></div>

padding-left: 0.166em;">&nbsp;</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-3485" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">2</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-3486" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">,</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-3487" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.348em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.453em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mi mathvariant="normal">f</mi><mrow><mo>(</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">x</mi><mo>)</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><mi>sin</mi><mo>⁡</mo><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mi mathvariant="normal">x</mi></mrow><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mo>;</mo><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><msup><mi mathvariant="normal">f</mi><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mn>4</mn><mi mathvariant="normal">n</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msup><mrow><mo>(</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">x</mi><mo>)</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><mi>cos</mi><mo>⁡</mo><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mi mathvariant="normal">x</mi></mrow><mo>;</mo><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><msup><mi mathvariant="normal">f</mi><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mn>4</mn><mi mathvariant="normal">n</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>2</mn></mrow></msup><mrow><mo>(</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">x</mi><mo>)</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><mo>−</mo><mi>sin</mi><mo>⁡</mo><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mi mathvariant="normal">x</mi></mrow><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mo stretchy="false">[</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">n</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn><mo>,</mo><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mn>1</mn><mo>,</mo><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mn>2</mn><mo>,</mo><mo>…</mo><mo stretchy="false">]</mo></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-191">\rm f\left(x\right)=\sin{x}\ ;\ \ f^{4n+1}\left(x\right)=\cos{x};\ \ f^{4n+2}\left(x\right)=-\sin{x}\ \ [n=0,\ 1,\ 2,\ldots]</script></span></p>

<p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-192-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><msup><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>f</mi><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mn>4</mn><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>n</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>3</mn></mrow></msup><mrow><mo>(</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>x</mi><mo>)</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mi>cos</mi><mo>&amp;#x2061;</mo><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>x</mi></mrow><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mo>;</mo><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><msup><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>f</mi><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mn>4</mn><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>n</mi></mrow></msup><mrow><mo>(</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>x</mi><mo>)</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><mi>sin</mi><mo>&amp;#x2061;</mo><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>x</mi></mrow></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-3489" style="width: 15.207em; <p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-193-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2234;</mo><msup><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>f</mi><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mn>11</mn></mrow></msup><mrow><mo>(</mo><mn>0</mn><mo>)</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><msup><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>f</mi><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mn>4</mn><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mn>2</mn><mo>+</mo><mn>3</mn></mrow></msup><mrow><mo>(</mo><mn>0</mn><mo>)</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mi>cos</mi><mo>&amp;#x2061;</mo><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mn>0</mn></mrow><mo>=</mo><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>1</mn></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-3530" style="width: 16.068em; </span>

                                        <div class="serial"><span>Question 25</span></div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p>যদি একটি সমবাহু ত্রিভুজের বাহুগুলো প্রতি সেকেন্ডে&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-194-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><msqrt><mn>3</mn></msqrt><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>c</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>m</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-3566" style="width: 3.504em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 2.871em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.269em, 1002.87em, 2.498em, -999.998em); margin-left: -0.162em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-275" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">5</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1000.33em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -3.645em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.162em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-276" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">2</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.904em, 1000.49em, 1.191em, -999.998em); top: -1.268em; left: 0em;"><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: 0em; border-top: 1.5px solid; width: 0.494em; height: 0px;"></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.068em;"></span></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.969em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.948em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 2.152em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><munder><mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">l</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">i</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">m</mi></mrow><mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">x</mi><mo stretchy="false">→</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow></munder><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mfrac><mrow><mo>−</mo><mn>2</mn><mi>sin</mi><mo>⁡</mo><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mn>2</mn><mi mathvariant="normal">x</mi></mrow><mo>+</mo><mn>3</mn><mi>sin</mi><mo>⁡</mo><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mn>3</mn><mi mathvariant="normal">x</mi></mrow></mrow><mrow><mn>2</mn><mi mathvariant="normal">x</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><munder><mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">l</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">i</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">m</mi></mrow><mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">x</mi><mo stretchy="false">→</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow></munder><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mfrac><mrow><mo>−</mo><mn>4</mn><mi>cos</mi><mo>⁡</mo><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mn>2</mn><mi mathvariant="normal">x</mi></mrow><mo>+</mo><mn>9</mn><mi>cos</mi><mo>⁡</mo><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mn>3</mn><mi mathvariant="normal">x</mi></mrow></mrow><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>5</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-12">\rm \underset {x\rightarrow0}{lim}\ \frac{-2\sin{2x}+3\sin{3x}}{2x}=\underset {x\rightarrow0}{lim}\ \frac{-4\cos{2x}+9\cos{3x}}{2}=\frac{5}{2}</script></span></p>
</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                                    <div class="row solveText" style="display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4;">
                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p>স্পর্শক ও অভিলম্বের ছেদবিন্দু&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-22-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mn>2</mn><mo>,</mo><mn>23</mn></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow><mo>,</mo><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>f</mi><mrow><mo>(</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>x</mi><mo>)</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>a</mi><msup><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>b</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>c</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-330" style="width: 12.174em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 9.961em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.027em, 1009.92em, 2.338em, -999.998em); top: -1.965em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-331"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-332"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-333" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">(</span><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-334"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-335" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">2</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-336" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">,</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-337" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.166em;">23</span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-338" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">)</span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-339" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.166em;">,</span><span class="mtext" id="MathJax-Span-340" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.166em;">&nbsp;</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-341" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">f<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.084em;"></span></span><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-342" style="padding-left: 0.166em;"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-343" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">(</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-344" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">x</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-345" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">)</span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-346" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.403em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mn>2</mn><mo>,</mo><mn>23</mn></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow><mo>,</mo><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mi mathvariant="normal">f</mi><mrow><mo>(</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">x</mi><mo>)</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">a</mi><msup><mi mathvariant="normal">x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">b</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">x</mi><mo>+</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">c</mi></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-22">\rm \left(2,23\right),\ f\left(x\right)=ax^2+bx+c</script></span>&nbsp;হলে&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; <p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-24-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>f</mi><mrow><mo>(</mo><mn>2</mn><mo>)</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><mn>4</mn><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>a</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>2</mn><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>b</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>7</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>23</mn><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>&amp;#x21D2;</mo><mn>4</mn><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>a</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>2</mn><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>b</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>16</mn><mo>&amp;#x2026;</mo><mo>&amp;#x2026;</mo><mo>&amp;#x2026;</mo><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>(</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>i</mi><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>)</mo></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-367" style="width: 22.912em; <p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-28-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mrow><mo>(</mo><mi>i</mi><mo>)</mo></mrow></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-447" style="width: 1.109em;
