<p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-31-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2234;</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>f</mi><mrow><mo>(</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>)</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><mn>9</mn></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-473" style="width: 4.674em;                                             <div class="input-group-append questionTable">
                                                <label style="margin-left:5px;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-37-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>3</mn></msup></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-522" style="width: 1.232em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.004em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.232em, 1001em, 2.325em, -999.998em); top: -2.184em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-523"><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-524"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.004em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.418em, 1000.5em, 4.146em, -999.998em); top: -4.005em; left: 0em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-525" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">x</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.01em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -4.369em; left: 0.594em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-526" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">3</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.01em;"></span></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.188em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.053em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.169em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>3</mn></msup></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-37"> x^3</script></span></p>
</label>
                                                
                                            </div>
                                        </div>

                                </div>

                            <div class="row question">
                                <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial"><span>Question 31</span></div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-43-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>f</mi><mrow><mo>(</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>x</mi><mo>)</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><msup><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>x</mi><mn>3</mn></msup><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>6</mn><msup><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mn>13</mn><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>x</mi><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>1</mn></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-671" style="width: 13.787em; padding-left: 0.207em;">−</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-759" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">2</span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-760" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">)</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -4.506em; left: 2.994em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-761" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">2</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-762" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">+</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-763" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">1</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-764" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">&gt;</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-765" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">0</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.051em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.497em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.702em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><msup><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">f</mi></mrow><mi class="MJX-variant" mathvariant="normal">′</mi></msup><mrow><mo>(</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">x</mi><mo>)</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><mn>3</mn><msup><mi mathvariant="normal">x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>−</mo><mn>12</mn><mi mathvariant="normal">x</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>13</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>3</mn><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><msup><mi mathvariant="normal">x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>−</mo><mn>4</mn><mi mathvariant="normal">x</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>4</mn></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>3</mn><msup><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">x</mi><mo>−</mo><mn>2</mn></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>&gt;</mo><mn>0</mn></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-45">\rm {\Rightarrow f}^\prime\left(x\right)=3x^2-12x+13=3\left(x^2-4x+4\right)+1=3\left(x-2\right)^2+1>0</script></span></p>

<p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-46-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2234;</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>f</mi><mrow><mo>(</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>x</mi><mo>)</mo></mrow></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-766" style="width: 2.83em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 2.297em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.314em, 1002.22em, 2.543em, -999.998em); top: -2.17em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-767"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-768" style="font-family: MathJax_AMS;">∴</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-769" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">f<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.084em;"></span></span><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-770" style="padding-left: 0.166em;"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-771" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">(</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-772" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">x</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-773" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">)</span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.174em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.348em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.302em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mo>∴</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">f</mi><mrow><mo>(</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">x</mi><mo>)</mo></mrow></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-46">\rm \therefore f\left(x\right)</script></span>&nbsp;ক্রমবর্ধমান</p>
</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="row questionBlock">

                            <div class="row question">
                                <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial"><span>Question 32</span></div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p>একটি m ফুট দৈর্ঘ্যের বাহু বিশিষ্ট সুষম ষড়ভুজের ক্ষেত্রফল বৃদ্ধির হার m ফুট/সেকেন্ড হলে তখন, বাহুর দৈর্ঘ্য পরিবর্তনের হার কত ফুট/সেকেন্ড?</p>

                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="row questionOptions">
                                    <div class="col-sm-12 row questionOption">
                                        <div class="input-group " style="align-items: center;">

                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p><img alt="" src="data:image/png;base64," style="width: 110px; height: 120px;"></p>

<p>6 টি সমবাহু ত্রিভুজ।</p>

<p>ক্ষেত্রফল&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-51-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>A</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><msqrt><mn>3</mn></msqrt><mn>4</mn></mfrac><msup><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>m</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mn>6</mn><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>3</mn><msqrt><mn>3</mn></msqrt></mrow><mn>2</mn></mfrac><msup><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>m</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-803" style="width: 10.699em; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -4.383em; left: 0.822em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-827" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">2</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.969em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.497em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.902em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mi mathvariant="normal">A</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><msqrt><mn>3</mn></msqrt><mn>4</mn></mfrac><msup><mi mathvariant="normal">m</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>×</mo><mn>6</mn><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>3</mn><msqrt><mn>3</mn></msqrt></mrow><mn>2</mn></mfrac><msup><mi mathvariant="normal">m</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-51">\rm A=\frac{\sqrt3}{4}m^2\times6=\frac{3\sqrt3}{2}m^2</script></span>&nbsp;</p>

                            <div class="row question">
                                <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial"><span>Question 33</span></div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-53-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><munder><mrow><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>l</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>i</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>m</mi></mrow><mrow><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>x</mi><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>&amp;#x2192;</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow></munder><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mrow><mn>2</mn><mo>+</mo><msup><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>e</mi><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>x</mi></mfrac></msup></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mo>?</mo></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-893" style="width: 6.634em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 2.202em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><munder><mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">l</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">i</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">m</mi></mrow><mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">x</mi><mo stretchy="false">→</mo><msup><mn>0</mn><mo>+</mo></msup></mrow></munder><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mrow><mn>2</mn><mo>+</mo><msup><mi mathvariant="normal">e</mi><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mi mathvariant="normal">x</mi></mfrac></msup></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mrow><mn>2</mn><mo>+</mo><msup><mi mathvariant="normal">e</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">∞</mi></msup></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-57">\rm \underset{x\rightarrow0^+}{lim}\ \frac{1}{2+e^\frac{1}{x}}=\frac{1}{2+e^\infty}=0</script></span></p>

clip: rect(3.169em, 1000.37em, 4.1em, -999.998em); top: -3.985em; left: 0em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1204" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">f<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.076em;"></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 3.988em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -4.357em; left: 0.449em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1205" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">′</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 3.988em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1206" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">(</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1207" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">x</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1208" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">)</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.237em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.361em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.32em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><msup><mi mathvariant="normal">f</mi><mi class="MJX-variant" mathvariant="normal">′</mi></msup><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">x</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-68">\rm f^\prime(x)</script></span> এর সর্বোচ্চ মান 3 হয়, তাহলে <span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-69-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi>f</mi><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>(</mo><mn>8</mn><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>)</mo></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1209" style="width: 2.275em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.865em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.38em, 1001.75em, 2.61em, -999.998em); top: -2.234em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1210"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1211" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">f<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.076em;"></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1212" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">(</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1213" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">8</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1214" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">)</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.237em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.361em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.32em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mi>f</mi><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mn>8</mn><mo stretchy="false">)</mo></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-69">f(8)</script></span> এর সর্বনিম্ন মান কত?</p>

                                        </div>
                                    </div>

                                    <div class="row solveText" style="display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4;">
                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p>Lagrange’s mean value theorem অনুসারে, এমন একটি বিন্দু <span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-74-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mi>c</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1230" style="width: 2.379em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.928em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.395em, 1001.93em, 2.092em, -999.998em); top: -1.965em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1231"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1232" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">x</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1233" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1234" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic; padding-left: 0.289em;">c</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.969em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.048em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 0.653em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mi>c</mi></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-74">x=c </script></span> বিদ্যমান যেন,&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-75-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><msup><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>f</mi><mi class=&quot;MJX-variant&quot; mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>&amp;#x2032;</mi></msup><mrow><mo>(</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>c</mi><mo>)</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>f</mi><mrow><mo>(</mo><mn>17</mn><mo>)</mo></mrow><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>f</mi><mrow><mo>(</mo><mn>8</mn><mo>)</mo></mrow></mrow><mrow><mn>17</mn><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>8</mn></mrow></mfrac><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>&amp;#x21D2;</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>f</mi><mrow><mo>(</mo><mn>8</mn><mo>)</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>f</mi><mrow><mo>(</mo><mn>17</mn><mo>)</mo></mrow><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>9</mn><msup><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>f</mi><mi class=&quot;MJX-variant&quot; mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>&amp;#x2032;</mi></msup><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>(</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>c</mi><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>)</mo></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1235" style="width: 17.83em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 14.592em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.74em, 1014.51em, 2.502em, -999.998em); top: -1.965em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1236"><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-1237"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.699em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.199em, 1000.37em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1238" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">f<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.084em;"></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -4.383em; left: 0.453em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1239" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">′</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1240" style="padding-left: 0.166em;"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1241" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">(</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1242" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">c</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1243" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">)</span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1244" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mfrac" id="MathJax-Span-1245" style="padding-left: 0.289em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 3.363em; height: 0px; margin-right: 0.125em; margin-left: 0.125em;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.363em, 1003.16em, 4.305em, -999.998em); top: -4.588em; left: 50%; margin-left: -1.596em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1246"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1247" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">f<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.043em;"></span></span><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1248"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1249" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">(</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1250" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">17</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1251" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">)</span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1252" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">−</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1253" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">f<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.043em;"></span></span><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1254"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1255" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">(</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1256" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">8</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1257" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">)</span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.404em, 1001.6em, 4.182em, -999.998em); top: -3.645em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.818em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1258"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1259" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">17</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1260" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">−</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1261" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">8</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.904em, 1003.36em, 1.191em, -999.998em); top: -1.268em; left: 0em;"><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: 0em; border-top: 1.5px solid; width: 3.363em; height: 0px;"></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.068em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1262" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">⇒</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1263" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">f<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.084em;"></span></span><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1264" style="padding-left: 0.166em;"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1265" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">(</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1266" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">8</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1267" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">)</span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1268" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1269" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">f<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.084em;"></span></span><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1270" style="padding-left: 0.166em;"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1271" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">(</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1272" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">17</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1273" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">)</span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1274" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">−</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1275" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">9</span><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-1276"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.699em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.199em, 1000.37em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1277" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">f<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.084em;"></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -4.383em; left: 0.453em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1278" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">′</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1279" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">(</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1280" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">c</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1281" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">)</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.969em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.547em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.952em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><msup><mi mathvariant="normal">f</mi><mi class="MJX-variant" mathvariant="normal">′</mi></msup><mrow><mo>(</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">c</mi><mo>)</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">f</mi><mrow><mo>(</mo><mn>17</mn><mo>)</mo></mrow><mo>−</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">f</mi><mrow><mo>(</mo><mn>8</mn><mo>)</mo></mrow></mrow><mrow><mn>17</mn><mo>−</mo><mn>8</mn></mrow></mfrac><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">f</mi><mrow><mo>(</mo><mn>8</mn><mo>)</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">f</mi><mrow><mo>(</mo><mn>17</mn><mo>)</mo></mrow><mo>−</mo><mn>9</mn><msup><mi mathvariant="normal">f</mi><mi class="MJX-variant" mathvariant="normal">′</mi></msup><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">c</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-75">\rm f^\prime\left(c\right)=\frac{f\left(17\right)-f\left(8\right)}{17-8}\Rightarrow f\left(8\right)=f\left(17\right)-9f^\prime(c)</script></span></p>

<p>এখানে,&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-76-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><msup><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>f</mi><mi class=&quot;MJX-variant&quot; mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>&amp;#x2032;</mi></msup><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>(</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>c</mi><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>)</mo></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1282" style="width: 1.928em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.559em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.068em, 1001.48em, 2.338em, -999.998em); top: -1.965em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1283"><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-1284"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.699em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.199em, 1000.37em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1285" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">f<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.084em;"></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -4.383em; left: 0.453em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1286" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">′</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1287" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">(</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1288" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">c</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1289" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">)</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.969em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.348em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.353em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><msup><mi mathvariant="normal">f</mi><mi class="MJX-variant" mathvariant="normal">′</mi></msup><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">c</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-76">\rm f^\prime(c) </script></span>&nbsp;সর্বোচ্চ হলে&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-77-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi>f</mi><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>(</mo><mn>8</mn><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>)</mo></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1290" style="width: 1.805em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.477em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.109em, 1001.39em, 2.338em, -999.998em); top: -1.965em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1291"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1292" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">f<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.043em;"></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1293" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">(</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1294" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">8</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1295" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">)</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.969em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.348em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.302em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mi>f</mi><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mn>8</mn><mo stretchy="false">)</mo></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-77">f(8)</script></span>&nbsp;সর্বনিম্ন হবে।</p>

<p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-78-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2234;</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>f</mi><mrow><mo>(</mo><mn>8</mn><mo>)</mo></mrow><mo>&amp;#x2265;</mo><mn>3</mn><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>9</mn><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mn>3</mn><mo>&amp;#x2234;</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>f</mi><mrow><mo>(</mo><mn>8</mn><mo>)</mo></mrow><mo>&amp;#x2265;</mo><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>24</mn></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1296" style="width: 14.264em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 11.682em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.314em, 1011.64em, 2.543em, -999.998em); top: -2.17em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1297"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1298" style="font-family: MathJax_AMS;">∴</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1299" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">f<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.084em;"></span></span><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1300" style="padding-left: 0.166em;"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1301" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">(</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1302" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">8</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1303" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">)</span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1304" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">≥</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1305" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">3</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1306" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">−</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1307" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">9</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1308" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">×</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1309" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">3</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1310" style="font-family: MathJax_AMS; padding-left: 0.289em;">∴</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1311" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">f<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.084em;"></span></span><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1312" style="padding-left: 0.166em;"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1313" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">(</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1314" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">8</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1315" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">)</span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1316" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">≥</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1317" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">−</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1318" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">24</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.174em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.348em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.302em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mo>∴</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">f</mi><mrow><mo>(</mo><mn>8</mn><mo>)</mo></mrow><mo>≥</mo><mn>3</mn><mo>−</mo><mn>9</mn><mo>×</mo><mn>3</mn><mo>∴</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">f</mi><mrow><mo>(</mo><mn>8</mn><mo>)</mo></mrow><mo>≥</mo><mo>−</mo><mn>24</mn></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-78">\rm \therefore f\left(8\right)\geq3-9\times3\therefore f\left(8\right)\geq-24</script></span></p>
</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                                    <div class="row solveText" style="display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4;">
                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-83-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>y</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>100</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mn>50</mn></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1343" style="width: 7.42em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 6.068em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.986em, 1006.03em, 2.461em, -999.998em); top: -1.965em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1344"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1345" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">x</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1346" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">+</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1347" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">y</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1348" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mfrac" id="MathJax-Span-1349" style="padding-left: 0.289em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.191em; height: 0px; margin-right: 0.125em; margin-left: 0.125em;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1001.03em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.424em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.531em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1350" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">100</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1000.33em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -3.645em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.162em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1351" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">2</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.904em, 1001.19em, 1.191em, -999.998em); top: -1.268em; left: 0em;"><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: 0em; border-top: 1.5px solid; width: 1.191em; height: 0px;"></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.068em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1352" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1353" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">50</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.969em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.497em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.602em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mi mathvariant="normal">x</mi><mo>+</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">y</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>100</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mn>50</mn></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-83">\rm x+y=\frac{100}{2}=50</script></span>, ক্ষেত্রফল&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-84-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo>=</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>x</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>y</mi><mo>=</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>x</mi><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mn>50</mn><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>x</mi></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><mn>50</mn><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>x</mi><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><msup><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1354" style="width: 12.707em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 10.412em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.027em, 1010.41em, 2.338em, -999.998em); top: -1.965em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1355"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1356" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">=</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1357" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">−</span><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-1372" style="padding-left: 0.207em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.945em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -4.383em; left: 0.535em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1374" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">2</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.969em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.348em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.403em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mo>=</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">x</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">y</mi><mo>=</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">x</mi><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mn>50</mn><mo>−</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">x</mi></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><mn>50</mn><mi mathvariant="normal">x</mi><mo>−</mo><msup><mi mathvariant="normal">x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-84">\rm =xy=x\left(50-x\right)=50x-x^2</script></span>&nbsp;</p>

<p>ক্ষেত্রফল সর্বোচ্চ হলে,&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-85-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mfrac><mrow><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>d</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>A</mi></mrow><mrow><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>d</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>x</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1375" style="width: 3.158em; <p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-86-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>&amp;#x21D2;</mo><mn>50</mn><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>2</mn><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn><mo>&amp;#x2234;</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>25</mn><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mo>,</mo><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>y</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>50</mn><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>25</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>25</mn></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1386" style="width: 18.855em;                                         <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-88-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>y</mi><mo>=</mo><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>(</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>)</mo><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>(</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>x</mi><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>1</mn><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>)</mo><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>(</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>x</mi><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>3</mn><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>)</mo><mo>=</mo><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>(</mo><msup><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>1</mn><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>)</mo><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>(</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>x</mi><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>3</mn><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>)</mo><mo>=</mo><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>(</mo><msup><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>x</mi><mn>3</mn></msup><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>3</mn><msup><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>3</mn><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>)</mo></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1428" style="width: 27.83em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 22.789em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.027em, 1022.71em, 2.338em, -999.998em);                                         <div class="serial"><span>Question 38</span></div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">

                                    <div class="row solveText" style="display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4;">
                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-98-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mfrac><mrow><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>d</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>x</mi></mrow><mrow><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>d</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>t</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mn>2</mn><mi>sin</mi><mo>&amp;#x2061;</mo><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>t</mi><mi>cos</mi><mo>&amp;#x2061;</mo><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>t</mi></mrow></mrow><mo>,</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>d</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>y</mi></mrow><mrow><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>d</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>t</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mi>sin</mi><mo>&amp;#x2061;</mo><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>t</mi></mrow></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1620" style="width: 12.707em; width: 0px; height: 1.068em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1707" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">sec</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1708"></span><span class="texatom" id="MathJax-Span-1709" style="padding-left: 0.166em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1710"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1711" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">t</span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.174em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -1.097em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 2.952em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mfrac><mfrac><mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">d</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">y</mi></mrow><mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">d</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">t</mi></mrow></mfrac><mfrac><mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">d</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">x</mi></mrow><mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">d</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">t</mi></mrow></mfrac></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mo>−</mo><mi>sin</mi><mo>⁡</mo><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mi mathvariant="normal">t</mi></mrow></mrow><mrow><mn>2</mn><mi>sin</mi><mo>⁡</mo><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mi mathvariant="normal">t</mi><mi>cos</mi><mo>⁡</mo><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mi mathvariant="normal">t</mi></mrow></mrow></mrow></mfrac><mo>∴</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">d</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">y</mi></mrow><mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">d</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">x</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mo>−</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mi>sec</mi><mo>⁡</mo><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mi mathvariant="normal">t</mi></mrow></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-99">\rm \frac{\frac{dy}{dt}}{\frac{dx}{dt}}=\frac{-\sin{t}}{2\sin{t\cos{t}}}\therefore\frac{dy}{dx}=-\frac{1}{2}\sec{t}</script></span>&nbsp;</p>

<p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-100-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2234;</mo><mfrac><mrow><msup><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>d</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>y</mi></mrow><mrow><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>d</mi><msup><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mi>sec</mi><mo>&amp;#x2061;</mo><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>t</mi><mi>tan</mi><mo>&amp;#x2061;</mo><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>t</mi></mrow></mrow><mfrac><mrow><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>d</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>t</mi></mrow><mrow><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>d</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>x</mi></mrow></mfrac></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1712" style="width: 10.453em; </span>

</label>

width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -4.219em; left: 0.371em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1862" style="font-size: 50%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">2</span><span style="display: inline-block;                                             </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="col-sm-12 row questionOption">
                                        <div class="input-group " style="align-items: center;">

                                                <label style="margin-left:5px;"><p>1</p>

</label>
                                                
                                            </div>
                                        </div>

                                    <div class="row solveText" style="display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4;">

<p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-124-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo>=</mo><mfrac><msup><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mn>1</mn><mo>+</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>x</mi></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow><mn>2</mn></msup><mrow><mn>2</mn><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mn>1</mn><mo>+</mo><msup><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow></mrow></mfrac><mfrac><mrow><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>2</mn></mrow><msup><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mn>1</mn><mo>+</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>x</mi></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow><mn>2</mn></msup></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mrow><mn>1</mn><mo>+</mo><msup><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></mrow></mfrac></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-2304" style="width: 10.535em; top: -1.965em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-2305"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-2306" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">=</span><span class="mfrac" id="MathJax-Span-2307" style="padding-left: 0.289em;"><span style="display: inline-block; clip: rect(3.404em, 1000.33em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -3.645em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.162em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-2593" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">4</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.904em, 1000.49em, 1.191em, -999.998em); top: -1.268em; left: 0em;"><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: 0em; border-top: 1.5px solid; width: 0.494em; height: 0px;"></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.068em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-2594" style="vertical-align: 0em;"><span style="font-family: MathJax_Size1;">)</span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-2595" style="vertical-align: 0em;"><span style="font-family: MathJax_Size1;">]</span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-2596" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-2597" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">12</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.174em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.497em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.602em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><msup><mi mathvariant="normal">e</mi><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mn>4</mn><mi mathvariant="normal">x</mi></mrow></msup><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>9</mn><mn>4</mn></mfrac><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><mn>4</mn><mi mathvariant="normal">x</mi><mo>=</mo><mi>ln</mi><mo>⁡</mo><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mrow><mo>(</mo><mfrac><mn>9</mn><mn>4</mn></mfrac><mo>)</mo></mrow></mrow><mo>∴</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">x</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>4</mn></mfrac><mi>ln</mi><mo>⁡</mo><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mrow><mo>(</mo><mfrac><mn>9</mn><mn>4</mn></mfrac><mo>)</mo></mrow></mrow><mo>∴</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">f</mi><mrow><mo>[</mo><mrow><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>4</mn></mfrac><mi>ln</mi><mo>⁡</mo><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mrow><mo>(</mo><mfrac><mn>9</mn><mn>4</mn></mfrac><mo>)</mo></mrow></mrow></mrow><mo>]</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><mn>12</mn></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-132">\rm \Rightarrow e^{4x}=\frac{9}{4}\Rightarrow4x=\ln{\left(\frac{9}{4}\right)}\therefore x=\frac{1}{4}\ln{\left(\frac{9}{4}\right)}\therefore f\left[\frac{1}{4}\ln{\left(\frac{9}{4}\right)}\right]=12</script></span></p>
</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

vertical-align: 0em; border-top: 1.5px solid; width: 10.33em; height: 0px;"></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.068em;"></span></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block;                         <div class="row questionBlock">

                            <div class="row question">
                                <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial"><span>Question 45</span></div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p>সমকোণী ত্রিভুজের একটি লম্বের দৈর্ঘ্য 4 একক এবং b একক দৈর্ঘ্যের অপর একটি বাহু সময়ের সাথে সাথে পরিবর্তিত হলে ত্রিভুজটির লম্বের বিপরীত কোণ পরিবর্তনের হার b বাহুর দৈর্ঘ্য পরিবর্তনের কত গুণ?</p>

clip: rect(0.904em, 1000.9em, 1.191em, -999.998em); top: -1.268em; left: 0em;"><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: 0em; border-top: 1.5px solid; width: 0.904em; height: 0px;"></span><span style="display: inline-block; vertical-align: -1.248em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 2.702em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mi>θ</mi><mo>=</mo><msup><mi>tan</mi><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msup><mo>⁡</mo><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mfrac><mn>4</mn><mi mathvariant="normal">b</mi></mfrac></mrow><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mo>∴</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">d</mi><mi>θ</mi></mrow><mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">d</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">t</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mrow><mn>1</mn><mo>+</mo><mfrac><mn>16</mn><msup><mi mathvariant="normal">b</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></mfrac></mrow></mfrac><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mo>−</mo><mfrac><mn>4</mn><msup><mi mathvariant="normal">b</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></mfrac></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow><mo>⋅</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">d</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">b</mi></mrow><mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">d</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">t</mi></mrow></mfrac></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-147">\rm \theta=\tan^{-1}{\frac{4}{b}}\ \therefore\frac{d\theta}{dt}=\frac{1}{1+\frac{16}{b^2}}\ \left(-\frac{4}{b^2}\right)\cdot\frac{db}{dt}</script></span></p>

<p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-148-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mfrac><mrow><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>d</mi><mi>&amp;#x03B8;</mi></mrow><mrow><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>d</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>t</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mfrac><mn>4</mn><mrow><msup><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>b</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mn>16</mn></mrow></mfrac><mfrac><mrow><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>d</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>b</mi></mrow><mrow><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>d</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>t</mi></mrow></mfrac></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-2991" style="width: 6.764em; class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mi mathvariant="normal">p</mi></mrow><mi>tan</mi><mo>⁡</mo><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mi mathvariant="normal">p</mi></mrow></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow></mrow><mrow><msup><mi>sin</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>⁡</mo><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mi {p\rightarrow0}{lim}\ \ \ \left[\frac{\tan{p}-\sin{p}}{\sin{p}\tan{p}}\right]=\underset{p\rightarrow0}{lim}\ \frac{\sin{p}\left(1-\cos{p}\right)}{\sin^2{p}}=\underset{p\rightarrow0}{lim}\ \frac{1-\cos{p}}{\sin{p}}=\underset {p\rightarrow0}{lim}\ \frac{\sin{p}}{\cos{p}}=\frac{0}{1}=0</script></span></p>
</span>

                        </div>
                        <div class="row questionBlock">

                            <div class="row question">
                                <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial"><span>Question 48</span></div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p>যদি একটি সমবাহু ত্রিভুজের বাহুগুলো প্রতি সেকেন্ডে&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-162-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><msqrt><mn>3</mn></msqrt><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>c</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>m</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-3382" style="width: 3.504em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 2.871em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.269em, 1002.87em, 2.498em, -999.998em); top: -2.234em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-3383"><span class="msqrt" id="MathJax-Span-3384"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.343em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; padding-left: 0.207em;">8</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-3499" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">×</span><span class="msqrt" id="MathJax-Span-3500" style="padding-left: 0.207em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.355em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.24em, 1000.45em, 4.182em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0.822em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-3501"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-3502" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">3</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.609em, 1000.49em, 3.895em, -999.998em); top: -4.547em; left: 0.822em;"><span style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">–</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.076em, 1000.86em, 4.346em, -999.998em); top: -4.055em; left: 0em;"><span style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">√</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-3503" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-3504" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">12</span><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-3505"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.723em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1001.27em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="texatom" id="MathJax-Span-3506"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-3507"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-3508" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">c</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-3509" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">m</span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -4.383em; left: 1.273em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-3510" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">2</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-3511"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.355em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1000.37em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-3512" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">s</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -4.383em; left: 0.412em;"><span class="texatom" id="MathJax-Span-3513"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-3514"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-3515" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">−</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-3516" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">1</span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.969em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.497em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.902em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mi mathvariant="normal">A</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><msqrt><mn>3</mn></msqrt><mn>4</mn></mfrac><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><msup><mi mathvariant="normal">a</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">d</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">A</mi></mrow><mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">d</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">t</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><msqrt><mn>3</mn></msqrt><mn>4</mn></mfrac><mo>×</mo><mn>2</mn><mi mathvariant="normal">a</mi><mo>×</mo><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mfrac><mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">d</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">a</mi></mrow><mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">d</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">t</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><msqrt><mn>3</mn></msqrt><mn>4</mn></mfrac><mo>×</mo><mn>2</mn><mo>×</mo><mn>8</mn><mo>×</mo><msqrt><mn>3</mn></msqrt><mo>=</mo><mn>12</mn><msup><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mi mathvariant="normal">c</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">m</mi></mrow><mn>2</mn></msup><msup><mi mathvariant="normal">s</mi><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msup></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-167">\rm A=\frac{\sqrt3}{4}\ a^2\Rightarrow\frac{dA}{dt}=\frac{\sqrt3}{4}\times2a\times\ \frac{da}{dt}=\frac{\sqrt3}{4}\times2\times8\times\sqrt3=12{\rm cm}^2s^{-1}</script></span></p>
</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="row questionBlock">

                            <div class="row question">

                                    <div class="row solveText" style="display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4;">
                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p>t তম সময়ে অবস্থান,&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-175-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mover><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>s</mi><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>&amp;#x2192;</mo></mover></mrow><mrow><mo>(</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>t</mi><mo>)</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>t</mi><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mover><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>i</mi><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>&amp;#x005E;</mo></mover></mrow><mo>+</mo><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><msup><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>t</mi><mn>5</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>t</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mover><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>j</mi><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>&amp;#x005E;</mo></mover></mrow></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-3551" style="width: 10.863em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 8.895em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.986em, 1008.77em, 2.543em, -999.998em); top: -2.047em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-3552"><span class="texatom" id="MathJax-Span-3553"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-3554"><span class="munderover" id="MathJax-Span-3555"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.412em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1000.37em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-3556" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">s</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -4.055em; left: -0.039em;"><span style="height: 0em; vertical-align: 0em; width: 0.453em; display: inline-block; overflow: hidden;"></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-3557" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">⃗&nbsp;<span style="height: 0em; vertical-align: 0em; margin-left: -0.203em;"></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0em;"></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-3558" style="padding-left: 0.166em;"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-3559" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">(</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-3560" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">t</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-3561" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">)</span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-3562" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; <p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-176-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2234;</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>d</mi><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mover><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>s</mi><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>&amp;#x2192;</mo></mover></mrow></mrow><mrow><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>d</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>t</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mover><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>v</mi><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>&amp;#x2192;</mo></mover></mrow><mo>=</mo><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mover><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>i</mi><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>&amp;#x005E;</mo></mover></mrow><mo>+</mo><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mn>5</mn><msup><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>t</mi><mn>4</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mover><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>j</mi><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>&amp;#x005E;</mo></mover></mrow></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-3586" style="width: 11.559em; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -4.014em; left: 0.043em;"><span style="height: 0em; vertical-align: 0em; width: 0.453em; display: inline-block; overflow: hidden;"></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-3661" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">⃗&nbsp;<span style="height: 0em; vertical-align: 0em; margin-left: -0.203em;"></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0em;"></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-3662" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">|</span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-3663" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-3664" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">81.006</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.174em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.348em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.552em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mover><mi mathvariant="normal">v</mi><mo stretchy="false">→</mo></mover></mrow><mo>=</mo><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mover><mi mathvariant="normal">i</mi><mo stretchy="false">^</mo></mover></mrow><mo>+</mo><mn>81</mn><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mover><mi mathvariant="normal">j</mi><mo stretchy="false">^</mo></mover></mrow><mo>∴</mo><mrow><mo>|</mo><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mover><mi mathvariant="normal">v</mi><mo stretchy="false">→</mo></mover></mrow><mo>|</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><mn>81.006</mn></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-178">\rm \vec{v}=\hat{i}+81\hat{j}\therefore\left|\vec{v}\right|=81.006</script></span></p>
</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="row questionBlock">

                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-7-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><msup><mi>x</mi><mi>y</mi></msup><mo>=</mo><msup><mi>e</mi><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mi>y</mi></mrow></msup><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>&amp;#x21D2;</mo><mi>y</mi><mi>l</mi><mi>n</mi><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mi>y</mi><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>&amp;#x21D2;</mo><mfrac><mi>y</mi><mi>x</mi></mfrac><mo>+</mo><mi>l</mi><mi>n</mi><mi>x</mi><mfrac><mrow><mi>d</mi><mi>y</mi></mrow><mrow><mi>d</mi><mi>x</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>+</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi>d</mi><mi>y</mi></mrow><mrow><mi>d</mi><mi>x</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>&amp;#x21D2;</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi>d</mi><mi>y</mi></mrow><mrow><mi>d</mi><mi>x</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mi>y</mi></mrow><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>(</mo><mi>l</mi><mi>n</mi><mi>x</mi><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>1</mn><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>)</mo></mrow></mfrac></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-84" style="width: 29.1em; width: 0px; height: 1.068em;"></span></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.969em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.747em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 2.052em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><msup><mi>x</mi><mi>y</mi></msup><mo>=</mo><msup><mi>e</mi><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mi>y</mi></mrow></msup><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><mi>y</mi><mi>l</mi><mi>n</mi><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mi>y</mi><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><mfrac><mi>y</mi><mi>x</mi></mfrac><mo>+</mo><mi>l</mi><mi>n</mi><mi>x</mi><mfrac><mrow><mi>d</mi><mi>y</mi></mrow><mrow><mi>d</mi><mi>x</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>+</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi>d</mi><mi>y</mi></mrow><mrow><mi>d</mi><mi>x</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi>d</mi><mi>y</mi></mrow><mrow><mi>d</mi><mi>x</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>−</mo><mi>y</mi></mrow><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>l</mi><mi>n</mi><mi>x</mi><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn><mo stretchy="false">)</mo></mrow></mfrac></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-7">x^y=e^{x+y}\Rightarrow ylnx=x+y 
\Rightarrow\frac{y}{x}+lnx\frac{dy}{dx}=1+\frac{dy}{dx}\Rightarrow\frac{dy}{dx}=\frac{x-y}{x(lnx-1)} 
</script></span></p>

width: 0.699em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; font-family: MathJax_Main; top: -4.014em; left: -0.08em;">−<span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; font-family: MathJax_Main; top: -4.014em; left: 0.002em;">−<span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.076em, 1000.86em, 4.346em, -999.998em); top: -3.932em; left: 0em;"><span style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">√</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-265" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">.</span><span class="mtext" id="MathJax-Span-266" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.166em;">&nbsp;</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-267" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">l</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-268" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">n</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-269" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">2</span><span class="mtext" id="MathJax-Span-270" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">&nbsp;</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.969em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -1.248em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 2.652em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mfrac><mrow><mi>d</mi><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><msup><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mn>2</mn></mrow><mi>x</mi></msup><mo stretchy="false">)</mo></mrow><mrow><mi>d</mi><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><msqrt><mi>x</mi></msqrt><mo stretchy="false">)</mo></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><msup><mn>2</mn><mi>x</mi></msup><mi>l</mi><mi>n</mi><mn>2</mn></mrow><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mrow><mn>2</mn><msqrt><mi>x</mi></msqrt></mrow></mfrac></mfrac><mo>=</mo><msup><mn>2</mn><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msup><msqrt><mi>x</mi></msqrt><mo>.</mo><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mi>l</mi><mi>n</mi><mn>2</mn><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-14"> 
\frac{d({\ 2}^x)}{d(\sqrt x)}=\frac{2^xln2}{\frac{1}{2\sqrt x}}=2^{x+1}\sqrt x.\ ln2\  
</script></span></p>
</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="row questionBlock">

                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
