border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 5.452em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mi>y</mi><mo>=</mo><munder><mo form="prefix">lim</mo><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="false">→</mo><mo>−</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">∞</mi></mrow></munder><msup><mrow><mo>(</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mi>x</mi></mfrac><mo>)</mo></mrow><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mo>−</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mi>x</mi></mfrac></mrow></msup><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><mi>l</mi><mi>n</mi><mi>y</mi><mo>=</mo><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mo>−</mo><munder><mo form="prefix">lim</mo><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="false">→</mo><mo>−</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">∞</mi></mrow></munder><mfrac><mrow><mi>ln</mi><mo>⁡</mo><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mrow><mo>(</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mi>x</mi></mfrac><mo>)</mo></mrow></mrow></mrow><mi>x</mi></mfrac><mspace linebreak="newline"></mspace><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><mi>l</mi><mi>n</mi><mi>y</mi><mo>=</mo><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mo>−</mo><munder><mo form="prefix">lim</mo><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="false">→</mo><mo>−</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">∞</mi></mrow></munder><mi>x</mi><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mo>−</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></mfrac></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><munder><mo form="prefix">lim</mo><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="false">→</mo><mo>−</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">∞</mi></mrow></munder><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mi>x</mi></mfrac></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-20">y= \underset{x\rightarrow-\infty}{\lim}  \left(\frac{1}{x}\right)^{-\frac{1}{x}}\Rightarrow lny=\ -   \underset{x\rightarrow-\infty}{\lim}  \frac{\ln{\left(\frac{1}{x}\right)}}{x}\\

\Rightarrow lny=\ - \underset{x\rightarrow-\infty}{\lim}  x\left(-\frac{1}{x^2}\right)= \underset{x\rightarrow-\infty}{\lim} \frac{1}{x}</script></span></p>

<p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-21-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2234;</mo><mi>y</mi><mo>=</mo><munder><mo form=&quot;prefix&quot;>lim</mo><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>&amp;#x2192;</mo><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>&amp;#x221E;</mi></mrow></munder><msup><mrow><mo>(</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mi>x</mi></mfrac><mo>)</mo></mrow><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mn>1</mn><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mo>/</mo></mrow><mi>x</mi></mrow></msup><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-400" style="width: 10.822em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 8.855em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.945em, 1008.77em, 3.035em, -999.998em); top: -2.17em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-401"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-402" style="font-family: MathJax_AMS;">∴</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-403" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic; padding-left: 0.289em;">y<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.002em;"></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-404" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="munder" id="MathJax-Span-405" style="padding-left: 0.289em;"><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.486em, 1002.34em, 4.305em, -999.998em); top: -3.4em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-407"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-408" style="font-size: 70.7%; margin-left: -0.162em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-416" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">1</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute;                                                 <label style="margin-left:5px;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-26-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi>sec</mi><mo>&amp;#x2061;</mo><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mi>x</mi></mrow><mi>tan</mi><mo>&amp;#x2061;</mo><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mi>x</mi></mrow></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-481" style="width: 5.421em; width: 0px; height: 2.174em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.547em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.852em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mi>y</mi><mo>=</mo><mi>ln</mi><mo>⁡</mo><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>s</mi><mi>e</mi><mi>c</mi><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mi>t</mi><mi>a</mi><mi>n</mi><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mo>∴</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi>d</mi><mi>y</mi></mrow><mrow><mi>d</mi><mi>x</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi>s</mi><mi>e</mi><mi>c</mi><mi>x</mi><mi>t</mi><mi>a</mi><mi>n</mi><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><msup><mi>sec</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>⁡</mo><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mi>x</mi></mrow></mrow><mrow><mi>s</mi><mi>e</mi><mi>c</mi><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mi>t</mi><mi>a</mi><mi>n</mi><mi>x</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mi>s</mi><mi>e</mi><mi>c</mi><mi>x</mi></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-27">
y=\ln(secx+tanx) 
\therefore\frac{dy}{dx}=\frac{secxtanx+\sec^2{x}}{secx+tanx}=secx 
</script></span></p>
</span>

<p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-36-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2234;</mo><munder><mo form=&quot;prefix&quot;>lim</mo><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>&amp;#x2192;</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow></munder><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>3</mn></msup><mi>cos</mi><mo>&amp;#x2061;</mo><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mrow><mo>(</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mi>x</mi></mfrac><mo>)</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-656" style="width: 8.814em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 7.215em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.191em, 1007.17em, 3.035em, -999.998em); top: -2.17em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-657"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-658" style="font-family: MathJax_AMS;">∴</span><span class="munder" id="MathJax-Span-659" style="padding-left: 0.289em;"><span style="display: inline-block;                                     <div class="row solveText" style="display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4;">
                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-42-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><munder><mo form=&quot;prefix&quot;>lim</mo><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>&amp;#x2192;</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>&amp;#x221E;</mi></mrow></munder><msup><mrow><mo>(</mo><mfrac><mi>x</mi><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></mfrac><mo>)</mo></mrow><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>3</mn><mi>x</mi></mrow></msup><mo>=</mo><munder><mo form=&quot;prefix&quot;>lim</mo><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>&amp;#x2192;</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>&amp;#x221E;</mi></mrow></munder><msup><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mn>1</mn><mo>+</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mi>x</mi></mfrac></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mn>3</mn><mi>x</mi></mrow></msup><mo>=</mo><msup><mi>e</mi><mn>3</mn></msup></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-725" style="width: 15.781em; </span>

top: -4.219em; left: 0.412em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-935" style="font-size: 50%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">2</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.904em, 1001.72em, 1.191em, -999.998em); top: -1.268em; left: 0em;"><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: 0em; border-top: 1.5px solid; width: 1.723em; height: 0px;"></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.068em;"></span></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.174em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.948em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 2.502em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mi>y</mi><mo>=</mo><msup><mi>tan</mi><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msup><mo>⁡</mo><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mfrac><mrow><mi>a</mi><mo>+</mo><mi>b</mi><mi>x</mi></mrow><mrow><mi>b</mi><mo>−</mo><mi>a</mi><mi>x</mi></mrow></mfrac></mrow><mo>=</mo><msup><mi>tan</mi><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msup><mo>⁡</mo><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mfrac><mrow><mfrac><mi>a</mi><mi>b</mi></mfrac><mo>+</mo><mi>x</mi></mrow><mrow><mn>1</mn><mo>−</mo><mfrac><mi>a</mi><mi>b</mi></mfrac><mi>x</mi></mrow></mfrac></mrow><mo>=</mo><msup><mi>tan</mi><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msup><mo>⁡</mo><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mfrac><mi>a</mi><mi>b</mi></mfrac><mo>+</mo><msup><mi>tan</mi><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msup><mo>⁡</mo><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mi>x</mi></mrow></mrow><mo>∴</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi>d</mi><mi>y</mi></mrow><mrow><mi>d</mi><mi>x</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mrow><mn>1</mn><mo>+</mo><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></mrow></mfrac></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-48">y=\tan^{-1}{\frac{a+bx}{b-ax}}=\tan^{-1}{\frac{\frac{a}{b}+x}{1-\frac{a}{b}x}}=\tan^{-1}{\frac{a}{b}+\tan^{-1}{x}} 
\therefore\frac{dy}{dx}=\frac{1}{1+x^2} 
</script></span></p>

width: 0px; height: 1.068em;"></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.904em, 1002.09em, 1.191em, -999.998em); width: 0px; height: 1.068em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1077" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1078" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic; width: 0px; height: 2.051em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -1.097em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 2.752em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><munder><mo form="prefix">lim</mo><mrow><mi>h</mi><mo stretchy="false">→</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow></munder><mfrac><mrow><mi>sin</mi><mo>⁡</mo><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mi>n</mi><mi>h</mi></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow></mrow><mo>−</mo><mi>s</mi><mi>i</mi><mi>n</mi><mi>x</mi></mrow><mrow><mi>n</mi><mi>h</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><munder><mo form="prefix">lim</mo><mrow><mi>n</mi><mi>h</mi><mo stretchy="false">→</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow></munder><mi>cos</mi><mo>⁡</mo><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi>n</mi><mi>h</mi></mrow><mn>2</mn></mfrac></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow></mrow><mfrac><mrow><mi>sin</mi><mo>⁡</mo><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mfrac><mrow><mi>n</mi><mi>h</mi></mrow><mn>2</mn></mfrac></mrow></mrow><mfrac><mrow><mi>n</mi><mi>h</mi></mrow><mn>2</mn></mfrac></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mi>c</mi><mi>o</mi><mi>s</mi><mi>x</mi></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-55">\underset{h\rightarrow0}{\lim} \frac{\sin{\left(x+nh\right)}-sinx}{nh}= 
\underset{nh\rightarrow0}{\lim}
\cos{\left(x+\frac{nh}{2}\right)}\frac{\sin{\frac{nh}{2}}}{\frac{nh}{2}}=cosx</script></span></p>

                            <div class="row question">
                                <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial"><span>Question 60</span></div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-64-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi>y</mi><mo>=</mo><mi>cos</mi><mo>&amp;#x2061;</mo><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>(</mo><mn>3</mn><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>5</mn><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>)</mo></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1230" style="width: 8.199em; top: -2.234em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1231"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1232" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">y<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden;                                         <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-72-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><msup><mi>f</mi><mi class=&quot;MJX-variant&quot; <p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-73-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2234;</mo><msup><mi>f</mi><mi class=&quot;MJX-variant&quot; top: -2.17em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1391"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1392" style="font-family: MathJax_AMS;">∴</span><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-1393" style="padding-left: 0.289em;"><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.043em;"></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -4.383em; left: 0.617em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1395" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">′</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1396" style="padding-left: 0.166em;"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1397" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">(</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1398" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">1</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1399" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">)</span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1400" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">−</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1404" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">6</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1405" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.348em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.353em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mo>∴</mo><msup><mi>f</mi><mi class="MJX-variant" mathvariant="normal">′</mi></msup><mrow><mo>(</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>)</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mn>3</mn><mo>−</mo><mn>6</mn><mo>=</mo><mo>−</mo><mn>3</mn><mo>&lt;</mo><mn>0</mn></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-73">\therefore f^\prime\left(1\right)=\ 3-6=-3<0</script></span>;&nbsp;ক্রমহ্রাসমান।</p>

                            <div class="row question">
                                <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial"><span>Question 62</span></div>

                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>

y=\left(\cos^{-1}{x}\right)^2\Rightarrow y_1=2\cos^{-1}{x}.  \frac{-1}{\sqrt{1-x^2}}\\
\Rightarrow\left(1-x^2\right)y_1^2=4y\Rightarrow\left(1-x^2\right)y_2-xy_1=2 
</script></span></p>

                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial"><span>Question 63</span></div>

                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>

f\left(2\right)=4a+2b+c=58\ldots\ldots(ii) \\
f^\prime\left(2\right)=4a+b=0\ldots\ldots(iii) \\
\left(i\right),\ \left(ii\right)\ \&\ \left(iii\right)\Rightarrow a=\ -7,\ b=28,\ c=30 
</script></span></p>

                                <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial"><span>Question 64</span></div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">

font-family: MathJax_Main;">1</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 3.988em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.392em, 1000.34em, 4.1em, -999.998em); clip: rect(0.859em, 1000.49em, 1.157em, -999.998em); top: -1.265em; left: 0em;"><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: 0em; border-top: 1.6px solid; width: 0.486em; height: 0px;"></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.045em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-1776"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.784em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.243em, 1000.34em, 4.1em, -999.998em); top: -3.985em; left: 0em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1777" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">t</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 3.988em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -4.357em; left: 0.374em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1778" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">2</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 3.988em;"></span></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.237em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.452em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.593em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mn>5</mn><mi>t</mi><mo>+</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><msup><mi>t</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-90">5t+\frac{1}{2}t^2 </script></span>&nbsp;ফুট দূরত্ব অতিক্রম করে। 2&nbsp;সেকেন্ডে &nbsp;<br>
ট্রেনের বেগ কত?</p>

                                    <div class="row solveText" style="display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4;">
                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-95-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi>S</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>5</mn><mi>t</mi><mo>+</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><msup><mi>t</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>&amp;#x21D2;</mo><mi>v</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>5</mn><mo>+</mo><mi>t</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1818" style="width: 11.068em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 9.059em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.986em, 1009.02em, 2.461em, -999.998em); top: -1.965em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1819"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1820" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">S<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.043em;"></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1821" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1822" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">5</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1823" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">t</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1824" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">+</span><span class="mfrac" id="MathJax-Span-1825" style="padding-left: 0.207em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.494em; height: 0px; margin-right: 0.125em; margin-left: 0.125em;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1000.29em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.424em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.162em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1826" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">1</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1000.33em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -3.645em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.162em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1827" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">2</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.904em, 1000.49em, 1.191em, -999.998em); top: -1.268em; left: 0em;"><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: 0em; border-top: 1.5px solid; width: 0.494em; height: 0px;"></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.068em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-1828"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.781em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.281em, 1000.33em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1829" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">t</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -4.383em; left: 0.371em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1830" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">2</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1831" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">⇒</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1832" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic; padding-left: 0.289em;">v</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1833" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1834" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">5</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1835" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">+</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1836" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic; padding-left: 0.207em;">t</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.969em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.497em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.602em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mi>S</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>5</mn><mi>t</mi><mo>+</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><msup><mi>t</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><mi>v</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>5</mn><mo>+</mo><mi>t</mi></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-95">S=5t+\frac{1}{2}t^2\Rightarrow v=5+t </script></span></p>

<p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-96-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2234;</mo><mi>t</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>2</mn><mi>s</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1837" style="width: 3.65em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 2.994em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.395em, 1002.95em, 2.379em, -999.998em); top: -2.17em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1838"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1839" style="font-family: MathJax_AMS;">∴</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1840" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic; padding-left: 0.289em;">t</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1841" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1842" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">2</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1843" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">s</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.174em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.148em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.002em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mo>∴</mo><mi>t</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>2</mn><mi>s</mi></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-96">\therefore t=2s </script></span>&nbsp;হলে,&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-97-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi>v</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>7</mn><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi>f</mi><mi>t</mi><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mo>/</mo></mrow><mi>s</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1844" style="width: 4.469em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 3.65em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.109em, 1003.61em, 2.338em, -999.998em); top: -1.965em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1845"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1846" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">v</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1847" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1848" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">7</span><span class="mtext" id="MathJax-Span-1849" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">&nbsp;</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1850" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">f<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.043em;"></span></span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1851" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">t</span><span class="texatom" id="MathJax-Span-1852"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1853"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1854" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">/</span></span></span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1855" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">s</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.969em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.348em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.302em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mi>v</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>7</mn><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mi>f</mi><mi>t</mi><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mo>/</mo></mrow><mi>s</mi></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-97">v=7\ ft/s</script></span></p>
</span>
                                    </div>

                                <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial"><span>Question 65</span></div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p><img alt="" src="data:image/png;base64," style="width: 250px; height: 207px;"></p>

<p>x&nbsp;এর কোন মানের জন্য&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-98-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi>g</mi><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>)</mo></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1856" style="width: 2.237em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.827em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.38em, 1001.72em, 2.61em, -999.998em); top: -2.234em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1857"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1858" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">g<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.002em;"></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1859" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">(</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1860" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">x</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1861" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">)</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.237em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.361em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.32em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mi>g</mi><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-98">g(x) </script></span>&nbsp;সর্বনিম্ন?</p>

                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>

\frac{dy}{dx}=\ -\frac{x+2}{y}\therefore m=\ -1 
</script></span></p>
</span>

                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>

width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 5.371em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -4.348em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 5.452em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mo>∴</mo><msup><mi>f</mi><mi>n</mi></msup><mrow><mo>(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>)</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><msup><mi>a</mi><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mi>n</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msup><mi>cos</mi><mo>⁡</mo><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mfrac><mrow><mi>n</mi><mi>π</mi></mrow><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mo>+</mo><mi>a</mi><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mi>b</mi></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow></mrow><mspace linebreak="newline"></mspace><mo>∴</mo><msup><mi>f</mi><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mn>10</mn></mrow></msup><mrow><mo>(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>)</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><msup><mi>a</mi><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mn>11</mn></mrow></msup><mi>cos</mi><mo>⁡</mo><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mfrac><mrow><mn>10</mn><mi>π</mi></mrow><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mo>+</mo><mi>a</mi><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mi>b</mi></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow></mrow><mo>=</mo><mo>−</mo><msup><mi>a</mi><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mn>11</mn></mrow></msup><mi>cos</mi><mo>⁡</mo><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mi>a</mi><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mi>b</mi></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow></mrow><mspace linebreak="newline"></mspace><mo>∴</mo><msup><mi>f</mi><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mn>10</mn></mrow></msup><mrow><mo>(</mo><mn>0</mn><mo>)</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><mo>−</mo><msup><mi>a</mi><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mn>11</mn></mrow></msup><mi>cos</mi><mo>⁡</mo><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mi>b</mi></mrow></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-125">\therefore f^n\left(x\right)=a^{n+1}\cos{\left(\frac{n\pi}{2}+ax+b\right)} \\
\therefore f^{10}\left(x\right)=a^{11}\cos{\left(\frac{10\pi}{2}+ax+b\right)}=-a^{11}\cos{\left(ax+b\right)} \\
\therefore f^{10}\left(0\right)=-a^{11}\cos{b} 
</script></span></p>
</span>

                            </div>
                        </div>

                <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                <br>
                <span style="color: black !important;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-62-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>t</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>a</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>n</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>A</mi><mo>=</mo><mi>tan</mi><mo>&amp;#x2061;</mo><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mrow><mo>{</mo><mrow><mi>&amp;#x03C0;</mi><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>B</mi><mo>+</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>C</mi></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow></mrow><mo>}</mo></mrow></mrow><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>t</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>a</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>n</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>B</mi><mo>+</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>t</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>a</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>n</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>C</mi></mrow><mrow><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>t</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>a</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>n</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>B</mi><mo>.</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>t</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>a</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>n</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>C</mi><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></mfrac></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-923" style="width: 17.215em; font-family: MathJax_Main;">B</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-964" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">.</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-965" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">t</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-966" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">a</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-967" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">n</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-968" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">C</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-969" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">−</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-970" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">1</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.904em, 1004.26em, 1.191em, -999.998em); top: -1.268em; left: 0em;"><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: 0em; border-top: 1.5px solid; width: 4.264em; height: 0px;"></span><span style="display: inline-block; vertical-align: -0.597em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.802em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mi mathvariant="normal">t</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">a</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">n</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">A</mi><mo>=</mo><mi>tan</mi><mo>⁡</mo><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mrow><mo>{</mo><mrow><mi>π</mi><mo>−</mo><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">B</mi><mo>+</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">C</mi></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow></mrow><mo>}</mo></mrow></mrow><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">t</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">a</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">n</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">B</mi><mo>+</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">t</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">a</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">n</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">C</mi></mrow><mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">t</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">a</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">n</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">B</mi><mo>.</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">t</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">a</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">n</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">C</mi><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></mfrac></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-62">\rm tanA=\tan{\left\{\pi-\left(B+C\right)\right\}}=\frac{tanB+tanC}{tanB.tanC-1}</script></span></p>

xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">t</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">a</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">n</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">B</mi><mo>+</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">t</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">a</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">n</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">C</mi></mrow><mfrac><mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">a</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">n</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">B</mi><mo>+</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">t</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">a</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">n</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">C</mi></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-63">\rm =\frac{tanB+tanC}{\frac{sinB.sinC-cosB.cosC}{cosB.cosC}}=\frac{tanB+tanC}{\frac{-\cos(B+C)}{cosB.cosC}}=tanB+tanC</script></span></p>
</span>
            </div>
    </div>

                                <h4>Extra</h4>

</label>

<p><strong>Alternative:</strong></p>

<p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-12-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>y</mi></mrow><mo>=</mo><mi>ln</mi><mo>&amp;#x2061;</mo><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mo class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mn>10</mn><mo stretchy="false">)</mo></mrow><mi>ln</mi><mo>⁡</mo><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mi>sin</mi><mo>⁡</mo><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mi mathvariant="normal">x</mi></mrow></mrow><mspace linebreak="newline"></mspace><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mi mathvariant="normal">y</mi></mfrac><mfrac><mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">d</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">y</mi></mrow><mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">d</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">x</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mi>ln</mi><mo>⁡</mo><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mrow><mo>(</mo><mn>10</mn><mo>)</mo></mrow></mrow><mo>×</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi>cos</mi><mo>⁡</mo><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mi mathvariant="normal">x</mi></mrow></mrow><mrow><mi>sin</mi><mo>⁡</mo><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mi mathvariant="normal">x</mi></mrow></mrow></mfrac><mspace linebreak="newline"></mspace><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">d</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">y</mi></mrow><mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">d</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">x</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mi>ln</mi><mo>⁡</mo><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mn>10</mn><mo stretchy="false">)</mo></mrow><mi>cot</mi><mo>⁡</mo><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mi mathvariant="normal">x</mi></mrow><mo>×</mo><msup><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mn>10</mn></mrow><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mi>ln</mi><mo>⁡</mo><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mi>sin</mi><mo>⁡</mo><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mi mathvariant="normal">x</mi></mrow></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow></mrow></mrow></msup></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-12">\rm y={10}^{\ln{(\sin{x)}}}\Rightarrow\ln{y}=\ln{\left(10\right)^{\ln{\sin{x}}}} \\
\Rightarrow\ln{y}=\ln{(10)}\ln{\sin{x}}&nbsp;\\
\Rightarrow\frac{1}{y}\frac{dy}{dx}=\ln{\left(10\right)}\times\frac{\cos{x}}{\sin{x}}&nbsp;\\
\Rightarrow\frac{dy}{dx}=\ln{(10)}\cot{x}\times{10}^{\ln{\left(\sin{x}\right)}}&nbsp;</script></span></p>
</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="row questionBlock">

                            <div class="row question">

                                    <div class="row solveText" style="display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4;">
                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>

                        <div class="row questionBlock">

                            <div class="row question">
                                <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial"><span>Question 74</span></div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-19-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>f</mi><mrow><mo>(</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>x</mi><mo>)</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><mn>5</mn><msup><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>10</mn><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>x</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-566" style="width: 9.018em; padding-left: 0.263em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-574" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.263em;">5</span><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-575"><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 3.988em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-578" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.225em;">−</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-579" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; (ii) \ y\frac{dy}{dx}=x \\
(iii) \ y\frac{d^2y}{dx^2}+\left(\frac{dy}{dx}\right)^2=1</script></span><br>
<strong>নিচের কোনটি সঠিক?</strong></p>

                                <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial"><span>Question 78</span></div>

</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="row questionBlock">
                                <div class="row  uddipokText" style="display: block;">
                                    <p><b>নিচের</b><b> উদ্দীপকের আলোকে পরবর্তী দুটি প্রশ্নের উত্তর দাও:</b></p>

<p><b><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-42-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>f</mi><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>(</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>x</mi><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>)</mo><mo>=</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>c</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>o</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>t</mi><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2061;</mo></mrow><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>x</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-937" style="width: 5.926em;                                     <div class="row solveText" style="display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4;">

\ y_2=m^2e^{mx}\therefore y_n=m^ne^{mx} </script></span></p>
</span>

                        <div class="row questionBlock">

                            <div class="row question">
                                <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial"><span>Question 82</span></div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p style="text-align: justify;">সরলরেখায় চলমান কোনো কণার t সময়ে অতিক্রান্ত দূরত্ব&nbsp;<br>
<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-61-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>s</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><msup><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>t</mi><mn>3</mn></msup><mn>3</mn></mfrac><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mfrac><msup><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>t</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>t</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1216" style="width: 9.95em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 8.161em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.157em, 1008.09em, 2.722em, -999.998em); top: -2.234em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1217"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1218" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">s</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1219" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.263em;">=</span><span class="mfrac" id="MathJax-Span-1220" style="padding-left: 0.263em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.71em; height: 0px; margin-right: 0.114em; padding-left: 0.207em;">2</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1277" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1278" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -1.948em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 3.103em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mi mathvariant="normal">v</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">d</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">s</mi></mrow><mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">d</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">t</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><msup><mi mathvariant="normal">t</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>−</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">t</mi><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><msup><mi mathvariant="normal">t</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>−</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">t</mi><mo>−</mo><mn>2</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn><mspace linebreak="newline"></mspace><mo>∴</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">t</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>2</mn><mi mathvariant="normal">s</mi></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-63">\rm v=\frac{ds}{dt}=1\Rightarrow t^2-t-1=1\Rightarrow t^2-t-2=0 \\ \therefore t=2s </script></span></p>
</span>

type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-69">\rm \lim\limits_{x \to \ a} \frac{x^\frac{7}{2}-a^\frac{7}{2}}{x^\frac{3}{2}-a^\frac{3}{2}}= \lim\limits_{\sqrt x \to  \sqrt a} \frac{\left(\sqrt x\right)^7-\left(\sqrt a\right)^7}{\left(\sqrt x\right)^3-\left(\sqrt a\right)^3}= \lim\limits_{y \to b} \frac{y^7-b^7}{y^3-b^3}\ ;\left[\sqrt x=y,\ \sqrt a=b\right]  \\
=\frac{\frac{d}{db}(b^7)}{\frac{d}{db}(b^3)}=\frac{7b^6}{3b^2}=\frac{7}{3}b^4=\frac{7}{3}\left(\sqrt a\right)^4=\frac{7}{3}a^2 </script></span></p>

                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-76-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>y</mi></msup><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mo>;</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>l</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>n</mi><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>y</mi></mfrac><mfrac><mrow><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>d</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>y</mi></mrow><mrow><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>d</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">y</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">x</mi></mfrac><mfrac><mrow><mn>1</mn><mo>−</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">y</mi><mi>ln</mi><mo>⁡</mo><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mi mathvariant="normal">x</mi></mrow></mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">y</mi></mfrac></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><msup><mi mathvariant="normal">y</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">x</mi></mrow></mrow></mfrac></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-76">\rm y={{x^x}^x}^{x\cdots\infty}=x^y\ ;ln\ y=y\ ln\ x\Rightarrow\frac{1}{y}\frac{dy}{dx}=\frac{y}{x}+ln\ x\frac{dy}{dx} \\
\Rightarrow\frac{dy}{dx}\left(\frac{1}{y}-\ln{x}\right)=\frac{y}{x}\Rightarrow\frac{dy}{dx}=\frac{\frac{y}{x}}{\frac{1-y\ln{x}}{y}}=\frac{y^2}{x-xy\ln{x}} </script></span></p>

                                            <p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-77-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>y</mi><mo>=</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>a</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>x</mi><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>(</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>+</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>x</mi><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>)</mo></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1764" style="width: 7.193em; (ii) মূলবিন্দুতে&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-79-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mfrac><mrow><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>d</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>y</mi></mrow><mrow><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>d</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>x</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mn>3</mn><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>a</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1790" style="width: 4.212em; (iii) মূলবিন্দুতে স্পর্শকের সমীকরণ&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-80-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>y</mi><mo>=</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>a</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>x</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1802" style="width: 3.504em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 2.871em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.678em, 1002.87em, 2.535em, -999.998em); top: -2.234em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1803"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1804" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">y</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1805" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.263em;">=</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1806" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.263em;">a</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1807" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">x</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.237em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.27em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 0.866em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mi mathvariant="normal">y</mi><mo>=</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">a</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">x</mi></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-80">\rm y=ax</script></span><br>
<strong>নিচের কোনটি সঠিক?</strong></p>
